cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.DS, cs.SE

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a reduction of a decidable theory to propositional logic. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of theorem provers in solving verification problems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses the reduction of a theory to a logic that can be used to decide a combination of theories. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses the complexity of the procedure used for the reduction. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses the practical advantages of the reduction technique in solving verification problems.
